    - Custom logging with level control implemented

11. ANDROID TAPJACKING
    Severity: 4.8 (Medium)
    Original Status: FAILED
    Current Status: ✅ RESOLVED
    
    Remediation Details:
    - android:filterTouchesWhenObscured="true" set on sensitive views
    - Overlay detection implemented
    - Window.FLAG_SECURE for sensitive screens
    - Touch event validation enabled

12. STRANDHOGG VULNERABILITY
    Severity: 6.5 (Medium)
    Original Status: FAILED
    Current Status: ✅ RESOLVED
    
    Remediation Details:
    - taskAffinity set to package name for all activities
    - launchMode properly configured
    - allowTaskReparenting="false" for sensitive activities
    - Activity intent validation implemented

13. JANUS VULNERABILITY (CVE-2017-13156)
    Severity: 6.7 (Medium)
    Original Status: FAILED
    Current Status: ✅ RESOLVED
    
    Remediation Details:
    - APK signed with V2 signature scheme
    - V1+V2 dual signing for compatibility
    - Verified via apksigner: "Verified using v2 scheme (APK Signature Scheme v2): true"
    - Protects against APK modification attacks

